Textometrica is a text analysis tool that can be used to analyse large amounts of text. You can examine the frequency of individual words, see how often one term is linked to another, and see which words together form ideas and concepts in the text. You can also create different visualisations and graphs in order to gain a better overview of the structure of your text.
Chorus running sentiment analysis on 90,000,000-row data set
Simon Lingren & Fredrik Palm  HUMLab University of Umea, Sweden
